cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a novel framework based on generative adversarial networks (GANs) to model label dependency for multi-label classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also extensively experiments and compares on two large-scale image classification benchmark datasets (MS-COCO and NUS-WIDE), indicating that it could belong to sub-categories such as cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
